        "TileImage": "$($repository 036b5b7f-7d2d-4514-bbe9-6f7c84a56f0e).Image",
        "Description": "My name is Michele Inversini, I run the Galeteria Bella. With a heavy heart I must make this request: Your target is a lady customer who frequently visits and has become an utter anoyance. Every visit she takes much too long deciding her order and delays the line of customers - I must get rid of her!\r\rYour job is to strike elusively with utmost precision. If all goes as planned, I have planted &quot;evidence&quot; and have a scapegat in mind - my tracks are covered!",
